==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tissued
<hw>Tis"sued</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Clothed in, or
adorned with, tissue; also, variegated; <as>as, <ex>tissued</ex>
flowers</as>.</def> <rj><au>Cowper.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And crested chiefs and <qex>tissued</qex> dames⟦br⟧
Assembled at the clarion's call.</q> <rj><qau>T. Warton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

